UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 341
1 accordance with subsections (3) to (6) of this section shall be deleted within seven
2 (7) days of the conclusion of any proceeding for which the images were retained.
3 Section 4. Whereas the safety of the Commonwealth's school children is of vital
4 importance, and it is imperative that the program to be developed under this Act start at
5 the beginning of the 2026-2027 school year, an emergency is declared to exist, and this
6 Act takes effect upon its passage and approval by the Governor or upon its otherwise
7 becoming a law.
